        "other_refer": [],
        "evidence": "<p>Fatty Liver Index (FLI) = e<sup>y</sup> / (1 + e<sup>y</sup>) &times; 100</p>\n<p>Where y = 0.953 &times; ln(triglycerides, mg/dL) + 0.139 &times; BMI, kg/m<sup>2</sup> + 0.718 &times; ln (GGT, U/L) + 0.053 &times; waist circumference, cm &ndash; 15.745</p>",
        "facts": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Interpretation:</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"126\" /><col width=\"126\" /><col width=\"200\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Fatty Liver Index</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Risk</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Diagnosis</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&lt;30</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Low</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Fatty liver ruled out (LR- = 0.2)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">30 to &lt;60</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Indeterminate</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Fatty liver neither ruled in nor ruled out</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&ge;60</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">High</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Fatty liver ruled in (LR+ = 4.3)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5cbef7af-e000-52c5-9e85-e54946e7918c\"></span><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5cbef7af-e000-52c5-9e85-e54946e7918c\"><br /></span></p>",
