        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar bmi = parseFloat(bmi);\nvar circ = parseFloat(circ);\nvar trig = parseFloat(trig);\nvar ggt = parseFloat(ggt);\n\nif (UOMSYSTEM == true) {\n\tcirc = circ / 0.39370079;\n    trig = trig;\n}\nelse {\n\tcirc = circ;\n  \ttrig = trig*88.57;\n}\n\nvar y = 0.953 * Math.log(trig) + 0.139 * bmi + 0.718 * Math.log(ggt) + 0.053 * circ - 15.745;\nvar fli = Math.exp(y) / (1 + Math.exp(y)) * 100;\n\nvar risk, msg;\n\nif (fli.toFixed(0) < 30) {\n\trisk = 'Low';\n\tmsg = 'Fatty liver ruled out (LR- = 0.2)';\n}\nelse if (fli.toFixed(0) >= 30 && fli.toFixed(0) < 60) {\n\trisk = 'Indeterminate';\n\tmsg = 'Fatty liver neither ruled in nor ruled out';\n}\nelse if (fli.toFixed(0) >= 60) {\n\trisk = 'High';\n\tmsg = 'Fatty liver ruled in (LR+ = 4.3)';\n}\n\ncalc_output.push({\n   name: 'mini',\n   value: fli.toFixed(0),\n   value_text: '',\n   message: risk + ' risk'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n   name: 'FLI',\n   value: fli.toFixed(0),\n   value_text: '',\n   message: 'Fatty Liver Index'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n   name: 'FLI',\n   value: risk,\n   value_text: 'risk',\n   message: msg\n});",
